            <p>Given the complexity of the analysis to be carried out, we have complemented the official data with the database of institutes specialized in territorial statistics. In the specific case of the aging data of the Spanish border municipalities, we have supplemented the official data with those from the Matrix Foundation and its interactive territorial maps (
