                </fig>
                <p>On the contrary, in the remaining municipalities the impact of depopulation is evident as traumatic. Thus, in the 
                    <xref ref-type="fig" rid="f4">Figure 4</xref> includes several border municipalities that in 1960 comfortably exceeded 1,300 inhabitants and that in 2020 move, almost all, below 500 inhabitants.</p>
