                                    <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="ref-32">Van Houtum, 2000</xref>: 64) individual or group that previously develops contacts that will lead them 
                                    <break/>to conclude agreements and contracts aimed at satisfying their needs, later. Simultaneously, it is exploring new 
                                    <break/>territories and opportunities in order to generate new contact and contract cycles.</td>
                            </tr>
