                                <td align="left" colspan="1" rowspan="1" valign="top">SOCIO-CULTURAL 
                                    <break/>APPROACH</td>
                                <td align="left" colspan="1" rowspan="1" valign="top">"homo socialis" so that their group perceptions (positive or negative) about the CBC will be conditioned by the 
                                    <break/>mutations that constantly take place in their changing "identity"</td>
